---

<Layout
  title="Stats & Systems"
  description="A numbers-first snapshot of who I am, what I track, and the rules I live by."
  pubDate="2025-11-17"
  heroImage="/images/about-lifeloggerz.gif"
  wide
  showViews={false}
>
  <div class="stats-page">
    <p class="intro">
      This page is my extended ‚ÄúAbout‚Äù ‚Äî not just who I am, but how I live:
      the numbers I track, the rules I follow, and the projects I‚Äôm actively
      building.
    </p>

    <!-- Snapshot Stats -->
    <section class="section" aria-labelledby="snapshot-heading">
      <h2 id="snapshot-heading">üìä Snapshot Stats</h2>
      <p class="section-hint">
        High-level stats pulled from my tracking sheets and logs. Not exhaustive
        ‚Äî just a glimpse.
      </p>
      <div class="grid stats-grid">
        {stats.map((item) => (
          <article class="stat-card">
            <div class="stat-icon" aria-hidden="true">{item.icon}</div>
            <div class="stat-label">{item.label}</div>
            <div class="stat-value">{item.value}</div>
            {item.note && <p class="stat-note">{item.note}</p>}
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Prohibitions -->
    <section class="section" aria-labelledby="prohibitions-heading">
      <h2 id="prohibitions-heading">üö´ Prohibitions</h2>
      <p class="section-hint">
        A lot of my productivity comes from what I <strong>don‚Äôt</strong> do.
        These constraints protect my time, focus, and identity.
      </p>
      <div class="grid prohibitions-grid" aria-label="List of prohibitions">
        {prohibitions.map((item) => (
          <article class="prohibition-card">
            <div class="prohibition-icon" aria-hidden="true">{item.icon}</div>
            <h3>{item.title}</h3>
            <p class="subtitle">{item.subtitle}</p>
            <p class="description">{item.description}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
      <p class="warning">
        ‚ö†Ô∏è Over time, you can become so productive that you end up scratching
        your head, wondering what to do next.
      </p>
    </section>

    <!-- Projects & Hobbies -->
    <section class="section" aria-labelledby="projects-heading">
      <h2 id="projects-heading">üß™ Current Projects & Hobbies</h2>
      <p class="section-hint">
        What I‚Äôm actively building or practicing outside of classes and lab
        work. These shift over time, but the themes stay similar: systems,
        learning, and craft.
      </p>
      <div class="grid projects-grid">
        {projects.map((p) => (
          <article class="project-card">
            <div class="project-header">
              <span class="status-badge">{p.status}</span>
            </div>
            <h3>{p.title}</h3>
            <p class="description">{p.blurb}</p>
            {p.tags?.length ? (
              <p class="tags">#{p.tags.join('  #')}</p>
            ) : null}
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>

  <style is:global>
    .stats-page {
      max-width: 960px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .stats-page .intro {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .stats-page .section {
      margin-top: 3rem;
    }

    .stats-page h2 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    .section-hint {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 0 auto 1.75rem;
      max-width: 640px;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(220px, 1fr));
      gap: 1.5rem;
    }

    /* Snapshot cards */
    .stat-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding: 18px 16px 16px;
      text-align: center;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.03);
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 4px;
    }

    .stat-icon {
      width: 56px;
      height: 56px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .stat-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }

    .stat-value {
      font-size: 1.25rem;
      font-weight: 800;
      margin-top: 0.1rem;
    }

    .stat-note {
      margin: 0.2rem 0 0;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    /* Prohibitions cards */
    .prohibition-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding: 18px 16px 16px;
      text-align: center;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.03);
    }

    .prohibition-icon {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 1.9rem;
      margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
      background: #0f172a;
      color: #ffffff;
    }

    .prohibition-card h3 {
      margin: 0.2rem 0 0.1rem;
      font-size: 1.02rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .prohibition-card .subtitle {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #6b7280;
      font-weight: 500;
    }

    .prohibition-card .description {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .warning {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      text-align: center;
      font-style: italic;
      color: #6b7280;
      max-width: 640px;
      margin-inline: auto;
    }

    /* Projects / hobbies */
    .project-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 18px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      padding: 18px 16px 16px;
      box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.03);
    }

    .project-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: flex-end;
      margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
    }

    .status-badge {
      font-size: 0.75rem;
      padding: 2px 8px;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: #e0ecff;
      color: #1d4ed8;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    .project-card h3 {
      margin: 0.25rem 0 0.35rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .project-card .description {
      margin: 0 0 0.5rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: #4b5563;
    }

    .project-card .tags {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      color: #6b7280;
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .stats-page .section {
        margin-top: 2.25rem;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
